name: Virginia G.
MessageText: Hello Steven,----Thank you for considering me for the job. Yes, I would like to write the article. If you start a contract, I'm ready to start immediately.----Best regards,--Virginia Gaces----Go to the proposal.

name: Joshua K.
MessageText: Hi Steven, thanks for the invite. I've been freelance writing for about five months and am familiar with the topic.----I'm great at doing research and spinning the information in an interesting way, especially when it comes to a topic I have personal experience with.----I could have an article of this size done by the end of the week - let me know if you'd like a few samples of my writing to see if I'd be a good fit.----Thanks again, and I hope to hear from you soon!----Best,--Josh----Go to the proposal.

name: Ria C.
MessageText: Good Day, Mr. Steven!----Thank you very much for the invitation.--Yes, I would love to collaborate with you on this project.--God bless you and your family!----All the best,--Ria----Go to the proposal.

name: Adrian B.
MessageText: Hi there, I'd definitely be interested in this. I've been freelancing for several years now and could bring a couple of interesting points and perspectives into this, perhaps also briefly discuss the "digital nomad" culture that's emerging. For writing gigs I normally charge a flat rate of $0.10 per word, so that would be $80 for 800 words, does work for you?----Adrian----Go to the proposal.

name: Haley S.
MessageText: Hello!----Thanks for reaching out. I'd love to help you out on this project.----Here are some samples of my work:----http://thenatpath.com/natural-news/vitamin-c-therapy/--http://thenatpath.com/natural-news/food-can-linings-contain-toxic-bpa-linings-study-finds/----You can also check out more samples in my profile.----Thanks!--Haley----Go to the proposal.

name: Hayley W.
MessageText: Hi, and thanks for the invitation to interview.----I am a native English writer, editor and proofreader from Australia.----I have a Certificate in Editing and Proofreading (distinctions) and am currently studying a Certificate IV in Professional Writing and Editing.----I have successfully completed many freelancing projects and you will see on my profile I have received excellent ratings and feedback.----I have written a number of blogs, articles, and web content, and can provide samples if required. I have also been freelancing full-time for over 12 months, so feel I am in a good position to write about the pros and cons of freelancing!----I am very interested in your proposal and would love to hear from you.----Regards, Hayley----Go to the proposal.

name: Lucy T.
MessageText: Hi Steven----Thanks for getting in touch, I'd love to write this article and definitely have plenty to say about the topic.----If there's any particular keywords, focus or format you'd like please just let me know.----Thanks----Lucy----Go to the proposal.

name: Chris S.
MessageText: Hi Steven,----Thank you for your invitation to interview. I would be happy to write about freelancing for your blog!----Would you please send me a link to other entries on your blog so I can get a sense for the style and tone you are look looking for?----Thanks!--Chris----Go to the proposal.
